DESCRIPTION:Block 1 (9:45–11:15): Active recall & light consolidation\, optionally with matcha.\n10-min break (11:15–11:25).\nBlock 2 (11:25–1:00 PM): Moderate study — practice problems\, concept mapping.\n\nPriority: High
RRULE:FREQ=DAILY;COUNT=30
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Study Block 1+2 starting — 90+10+90 min combined
TRIGGER:-PT10M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

